    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1216">
<l>naṉaveṉa voṉṟillai yāyiṉ kaṉaviṉāṟ</l>
<l> kātalar nīṅkalar maṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Were there no such thing as wakefulness, my beloved (who visited me) in my dream would not depart from me.</l>
            </lg>
